      • createElement

        public static Element createElement(Document doc,
                    String elementName)
        In the given MaryXML document, create a new element of the given name, with the proper namespace.
        Parameters:
        doc - a MaryXML document
        elementName - the name of the MaryXML document
        Returns:
        the newly created MaryXML element.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if the document is not a maryxml document with the proper namespace.
